trans-unit.source: The ActiveDirectoryPartition class is an abstract class that represents a directory partition in a domain.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ActiveDirectoryPartition er en abstrakt klasse som representerer en mappe partisjon i et domene.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryPartition"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryPartition"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Releases all managed and unmanaged resources that are held by the object.
trans-unit.target: Frigir alle behandlet ressurser som brukes av objektet.

trans-unit.source: Releases the managed resources that are used by the object and, optionally, releases unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: Frigir administrerte ressurser som brukes av objektet, og frigir eventuelt uforvaltede ressurser.

trans-unit.source: The `disposing` parameter only affects the release of the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Den `disposing` parameteren påvirker bare utgivelsen av de administrerte ressursene.

trans-unit.source: The unmanaged resources are always released by this method.
trans-unit.target: Ubehandlet ressursene frigis alltid av denne metoden.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Boolean> value that determines if the managed resources should be released.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Boolean>verdi som bestemmer om administrerte ressurser skal frigis.</xref:System.Boolean>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the managed resources are released; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if only the unmanaged resources are released.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis de administrerte ressursene er frigitt; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> Hvis bare uforvaltede ressursene er frigitt.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry"></xref> object that represents the directory partition.
trans-unit.target: Henter en <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry"> </xref> objektet som representerer directory partisjonen.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry"></xref> object that represents the directory partition.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry"> </xref> objektet som representerer directory partisjonen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that contains the partition name.
Retrieves a string representation of the current directory partition.
trans-unit.target: Henter en strengrepresentasjon av gjeldende mappe partisjon.

trans-unit.source: Returns a string representation of the current directory partition.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en strengrepresentasjon av gjeldende mappe partisjon.
